description.value: zcash.network is your first and best source for all of the information you’re looking for. From general topics to more of what you would expect to find here, zcash.network has it all. We hope you find what you are searching for!

description: Zcash is a privacy-focused cryptocurrency that allows transactions to be either transparent (like Bitcoin) or private using zero-knowledge proofs known as zk-SNARKs. This cryptography verifies transaction validity without exposing sender, recipient, or amount. As of 2025, approximately 20% of existing coins are shielded. The September 2025 launch of Zashi CrossPay enabled private cross-chain shielded swaps, significantly expanding Zcash's functionality for confidential transactions.
